First step :
	=> psql user creation:
		. sudo systemctl start postgresql.service
		. sudo -i -u postgres
		. createuser --interactive (has to be superuser)
		. createdb <db_name> (db_name = username)
LOG OUT 

Second step :
	=> linux user link:
		. sudo systemctl restart postgresql.service
		. sudo adduser <user_name> --disabled-login

Third step :
	=> psql as new_user:
		.sudo -i -u <user_name>
		.psql
